1 2.604698 2.444344 2.765051
2 4.226072 4.065719 4.386425
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
predict(sparrow_mod, newdata = new_x, interval = "prediction")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
